The foods and smoothies are awesome and so are the the owners and the rest of the staff!!! I usually get the large Green monster that comes with kale, bananas, blueberries, peanut butter, and honey, and I have them add strawberries to it. One quick story about the staff at Power Smoothie: About 1 1/2 years ago I was in the hospital with a serious medical condition. My daughter passed by to get me my green monster smoothie, and told them what happened to me and that I was in the hospital. My daughter brought me back the smoothie and it was signed by all of them saying get well soon, and they didn’t charge her for it. It definitely touched me and put a smile on my face! It was something small, but it meant a lot!!!
